#, no-wrap
msgid "Mutual TLS (mTLS) authentication"
msgstr "TLS互认证"

#: _versions/2.13/guides/security.adoc
msgid ""
"Quarkus provides mutual TLS (mTLS) authentication so that you can authenticate users based on their X.509 certificates.\n"
"For more information, see xref:security-built-in-authentication.adoc#mutual-tls[mutual TLS authentication]."
msgstr "Quarkus提供了TLS互认证，这样您就可以根据用户的X.509证书进行认证。更多信息请参见 link:security-built-in-authentication.html#mutual-tls[TLS互认证] 。"

#. type: Title ===
